snippet.title: The Game of Life (2016) - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
This is Marmalade Game Studio's first adaptation of the classic Hasbro game. This is much more smaller content-wise compared to its sequel, but it is still a fun game.

The Game of Life (C) Hasbro
Developed and published by Marmalade Game Studio
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/403120/THE_GAME_OF_LIFE/
